                                                                <img alt="HandpieceTraders.com" src="~/img/email/handpiece-traders-logo.jpg" width="400"></img>
                                                            </center>*@
                                                        </div>
                                                    </td>
                                                </tr>
                                                <tr>
                                                    <td style="background-color: black; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: white; padding-left: 60px; padding-right: 60px;">
                                                        <div style="text-align: center; color: white; line-height: 1; font-size: 1.75em; margin-top: 1em;">
                                                            Need More Genuine Handpieces
